Step 1: Download as Zip

Step 2: Go into the rar, then the Zip, then the RoProPlus-main, then the other Zip and drag the RoProPlus+ folder to your desktop

Step 3: Open your Browser and go to Extensions ( Click on Manage Extensions)

Step 4: Turn on Developer Mode and click on load unpacked extension

Step 5: In the Explorer window, go to Desktop, click once on RoProPlus+ and then on Select Folder

Now you have the free version of RoPro Plus / Rex which normally costs money :)
